@page "/blog"
@layout MainLayout


<h2 class="mb-4 animate__animated animate__fadeInDown">Family Travel Tips</h2>

<section class="blog-post container py-5">

    <h1 class="fw-bold text-primary mb-4 animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">
        Top 5 Family-Friendly Hotels in Boracay (Perfect for Kids & Parents)
    </h1>

    <p class="lead animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">
        Boracay isn’t just for couples and party-goers — it’s a <strong>fantastic family destination</strong> too!
        From White Beach sunsets to island-hopping adventures, your kids will love every moment.
        Here are the best <strong>family-friendly hotels in Boracay</strong> to make your vacation hassle-free.
    </p>

    <!-- Hotel #1 -->
    <div class="mb-5 animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">
        <h2 class="fw-bold">1. Henann Lagoon Resort</h2>
        <img src="/images/henanhotelblog.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded shadow mb-3" alt="Henann Lagoon Resort Boracay Family Hotel" />
        <p>
            Known for its huge lagoon-style pool, Henann Lagoon Resort is a
            <strong>family favorite</strong>. Spacious rooms, kid-friendly dining, and
            easy access to White Beach make it a top choice.
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Massive swimming pool with shallow areas for kids</li>
            <li>Family rooms available</li>
            <li>Walking distance to the beach</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Visit Official Website</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Hotel #2 -->
    <div class="mb-5 animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">
        <h2 class="fw-bold">2. Astoria Boracay</h2>
        <img src="/images/astoriahotelblog.jpeg" class="img-fluid rounded shadow mb-3" alt="Astoria Boracay Family Resort" />
        <p>
            Located in Station 1, Astoria offers <strong>quiet beachfront stays</strong> with
            plenty of room for families. Their pool and in-house restaurant make traveling with
            kids a breeze.
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Beachfront access</li>
            <li>Kids’ pool</li>
            <li>Spacious suites for families</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Visit Official Website</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Hotel #3 -->
    <div class="mb-5 animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">
        <h2 class="fw-bold">3. Crimson Resort & Spa Boracay</h2>
        <img src="/images/crimsonhotelblog.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded shadow mb-3" alt="Crimson Resort Boracay Family Stay" />
        <p>
            For families seeking luxury, Crimson Resort offers villas and suites with
            <strong>private pools</strong>. Their kids’ club ensures children are entertained
            while parents relax.
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Kids’ club with activities</li>
            <li>Private beach</li>
            <li>Luxury family villas</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Visit Official Website</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Hotel #4 -->
    <div class="mb-5 animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">
        <h2 class="fw-bold">4. Discovery Shores Boracay</h2>
        <img src="/images/discoveryhotelblog.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded shadow mb-3" alt="Discovery Shores Boracay Family Resort" />
        <p>
            A multi-awarded luxury resort with a <strong>reputation for excellent service</strong>.
            Families love the kids’ pool, beachfront suites, and dedicated staff for children.
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Beachfront family suites</li>
            <li>Kids’ pool and play area</li>
            <li>Award-winning service</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Visit Official Website</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Hotel #5 -->
    <div class="mb-5 animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">
        <h2 class="fw-bold">5. Fairways & Bluewater Boracay</h2>
        <img src="/images/fairwaybluewaterhotelblog.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded shadow mb-3" alt="Fairways and Bluewater Boracay Family Hotel" />
        <p>
            A massive resort with <strong>multiple pools, golf course, and a private beach</strong>.
            Families love its wide-open spaces and kids’ activities.
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Huge resort with multiple pools</li>
            <li>Kids’ club and play areas</li>
            <li>Private beach for families</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Visit Official Website</a>
    </div>

    <h2 class="fw-bold mt-5 animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">🌴 Family Travel Tips for Boracay</h2>
    <ul class="animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">
        <li>Stay in <strong>Station 1</strong> for quiet family-friendly vibes.</li>
        <li>Join an <strong>island-hopping tour</strong> (many include snorkeling and kid-safe activities).</li>
        <li>Travel during <strong>January–March</strong> for cooler weather and fewer crowds.</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="text-center mt-5 animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">
        <h3 class="fw-bold">Make Family Memories in Boracay 🌞</h3>
        <p>
            Boracay has something for everyone — from toddlers to grandparents.
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-lg btn-success">Contact Us for Booking Assistance</a>
    </div>
</section>
